      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── Schematics ─────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <div class="schematic-band">
    <div class="schematic-panel">
      <div class="schematic-panel-text">
        <div class="section-label">Aircraft Systems</div>
        <p style="font-size: 0.875rem;">From motor controllers to flight termination, Allocortech supplies complete power and avionics stacks for fixed-wing and rotary-wing platforms.</p>
