    <img src="/images/hero/section-bg.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" style="position: absolute; inset: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; opacity: 0.035; pointer-events: none;" />
    <div class="container">
      <div class="differentiators-grid">

        <div>
          <div class="section-label">03 / Why Allocortech</div>
          <h2 style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Small team.<br>Serious hardware.</h2>
          <p class="lead" style="max-width: 42ch; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
            Founded in 2018 by avionics engineers who saw what the UAS and eVTOL markets needed but weren't getting from legacy suppliers.
          </p>
          <a href="/about" class="btn btn-outline">About Allocortech</a>
        </div>

