              <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--ink-2);">New or custom designs from existing architectures in weeks, not months. MOTS solutions in 8–12 weeks. We move at startup pace.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="pillar" style="border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 0;">
            <span class="pillar-num">03</span>
            <div>
              <h4 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Unmatched Support</h4>
              <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--ink-2);">Support at a moment's notice. Engineering changes treated as normal, not as contract resets. We are an extension of your engineering team.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
